# CMake
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
install_manifest.txt
build*/

# libFuzzer findings from manual runs — reproducers stay out of history
crash-*
leak-*
oom-*
timeout-*

# Game assets — never commit copyrighted game content (see NOTICE). One
# pattern per extension documented in docs/fa/formats/ front-matter
# (regenerate: grep -h '^extensions:' docs/fa/formats/*.md), plus the game's
# own binaries and EA audio containers. Uppercase = FA asset extension; on a
# case-insensitive checkout (the Windows bench) these also match lowercase,
# so colliding repo file types are re-included at the end.
*.11K
*.5K
*.8K
*.AI
*.BI
*.BIN
*.CAM
*.CB8
*.CFG
*.DAT
*.DLG
*.ECM
*.FBC
*.FNT
*.GAS
*.HGR
*.HUD
*.INF
*.JT
*.LAY
*.LIB
*.M
*.MC
*.MM
*.MNU
*.MT
*.MUS
*.NT
*.OT
*.P
*.PAL
*.PIC
*.PT
*.PTS
*.RAW
*.RGN
*.SEE
*.SEQ
*.SH
*.SMS
*.SSF
*.T2
*.TXT
*.VDO
*.XMI
*.EXE
*.DLL
*.eac

# Repo file types the uppercase globs would otherwise shadow on
# case-insensitive checkouts:
!CMakeLists.txt
!requirements*.txt
!scripts/**/*.sh
!seed-*.bin
!tests/fixtures/**/*.bin

# Python bytecode cache (tools/*.py)
__pycache__/
